# ---------------------------
# CROS_COMMON_* : Dependencies common to all CrOS flavors
# CROS_E_* : Dependencies for embedded CrOS devices (busybox, no X etc)
# CROS_* : Dependencies for "regular" CrOS devices (coreutils, X etc)
